        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>This project involved developing a comprehensive content strategy for a SaaS platform, focusing on improving user engagement and simplifying product documentation.</p>

        <img src="../assets/img/project1-screenshot.jpg" alt="Project Screenshot">

        <h2>Challenges</h2>
        <p>One of the main challenges was transforming complex product features into easy-to-understand guides for a diverse audience. I collaborated with cross-functional teams to identify pain points and created detailed user manuals that streamlined the user onboarding process.</p>

        <h2>Tools Used</h2>
        <p>Figma, Adobe XD, Jira, Confluence, HTML, CSS</p>

        <h2>Outcome</h2>
        <p>The project resulted in a 20% increase in user engagement and improved customer satisfaction with the product documentation.</p>

